{"tid":898083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為咗九合一會飛轉台灣  有咩想知想睇？","createTime":"2018-11-11T12:18:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-11T17:44:22.000Z","uid":111657,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a6b9a0e2bf4084b34984e051d0ffca30646b2b6e","tid":898083,"uid":111657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T12:18:54.000Z","msg":"認真。如題。<br />\n22號出發，高雄台北都會去，24號當日就朝早喺高雄，中午到台北。<br />\n我自己主要目的就係觀察同感受下對岸嘅選舉氣氛。會同選民傾下計了解下佢地關心嘅議題，對台灣未來嘅睇法，之後影下相寫下文post喺自己facebook同朋友分享下咁。總之無乜特別嘅期待，睇下到時可以收穫到啲乜。<br />\n<br />\n開依個post係想問下大家，如果係你喺現場，除咗上網有得睇嘅選舉結果之外，你會有啲咩嘢想睇/想知/想問？<br />\n<br />\n多人覆嘅話盡量滿足，無人覆嘅話盡量update<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nGoogle有嘅嘢不作回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7ab4b9e56984da721b3548613c21a3669a0a0c6","tid":898083,"uid":55056,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T12:24:25.000Z","msg":"同你一樣 22號出發27號返 不過只去睇高雄"},{"pid":"82082a05fdc9b7ea70e26e17ee58fb9130af8551","tid":898083,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T12:34:41.000Z","msg":"選民最關注咩議題？有咩宣傳手法最引人留意？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4efdcb9e259ca4ddbc7de9b78cf193673c38db1f","tid":898083,"uid":1372,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c7ab4b9e56984da721b3548613c21a3669a0a0c6","tid":898083,"uid":55056,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T12:24:25.000Z","msg":"同你一樣 22號出發27號返 不過只去睇高雄"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T12:36:08.000Z","msg":"唔想個韓國魚做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfac21efec63c7fb707091bc7554203361460a7a","tid":898083,"uid":55056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4efdcb9e259ca4ddbc7de9b78cf193673c38db1f","tid":898083,"uid":1372,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c7ab4b9e56984da721b3548613c21a3669a0a0c6","tid":898083,"uid":55056,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"ci